<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>国土报最新头条</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 18 Oct 2023 00:30:59 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>“决心采取行动”：国会领导人承诺犹太组织全力支持以色列</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-18/ty-article/.premium/resolved-to-act-congressional-leaders-promise-jewish-groups-full-backing-for-israel/0000018b-4011-d242-abef-52372a5d0000</link><description>参议院多数党领袖查克·舒默誓言美国对以色列的紧急援助计划将“尽快”在国会获得通过</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Oct 2023 00:15:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-18/ty-article/.premium/resolved-to-act-congressional-leaders-promise-jewish-groups-full-backing-for-israel/0000018b-4011-d242-abef-52372a5d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列麦卡锡主义对其公民的迫害已经开始</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-18/ty-article-opinion/israels-mccarthyite-persecution-of-its-own-citizens-has-begun/0000018b-3f1a-d2b8-a7db-ff7faf310000</link><description></description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 23:41:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-18/ty-article-opinion/israels-mccarthyite-persecution-of-its-own-citizens-has-begun/0000018b-3f1a-d2b8-a7db-ff7faf310000</guid></item><item><title>拥抱之下，拜登和以色列之间正在酝酿紧张局势</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-18/ty-article-opinion/.premium/beneath-the-embrace-there-is-tension-brewing-between-biden-and-israel/0000018b-3e3c-d242-abef-7e3e480e0000</link><description>在哈马斯暴行之后，拜登政府迅速、全面、真诚和灵活地声援以色列。现在美国总统必须防止巴勒斯坦无辜者遭受灾难</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 22:12:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-18/ty-article-opinion/.premium/beneath-the-embrace-there-is-tension-brewing-between-biden-and-israel/0000018b-3e3c-d242-abef-7e3e480e0000</guid></item><item><title>就连内塔尼亚胡的忠诚者也背弃了他：“战争结束后，他必须走”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-18/ty-article/.premium/even-netanyahu-loyalists-are-turning-their-backs-after-the-war-he-has-to-go/0000018b-3ed1-d2b8-a7db-feffa3ca0000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡迫使我们组建一个极右翼政府，这在国家中造成了裂痕，并分裂了大部分人口。纳税人和在军队服役的人被排除在外。一名利库德集团官员表示，利库德集团草根阶层憎恶极端主义和极端分子。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 22:09:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-18/ty-article/.premium/even-netanyahu-loyalists-are-turning-their-backs-after-the-war-he-has-to-go/0000018b-3ed1-d2b8-a7db-feffa3ca0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列公众应该受到指责，而不是内塔尼亚胡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-18/ty-article-opinion/.premium/the-israeli-public-is-to-blame-not-netanyahu/0000018b-3ed6-d242-abef-7ef6991b0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 21:20:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-18/ty-article-opinion/.premium/the-israeli-public-is-to-blame-not-netanyahu/0000018b-3ed6-d242-abef-7ef6991b0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡将无法逃脱指责</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-18/ty-article-opinion/.premium/netanyahu-wont-be-able-to-escape-blame/0000018b-3ed6-d242-abef-7ef6971b0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 21:09:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-18/ty-article-opinion/.premium/netanyahu-wont-be-able-to-escape-blame/0000018b-3ed6-d242-abef-7ef6971b0000</guid></item><item><title>拜登为何访问战时以色列</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-17/ty-article/.premium/why-biden-is-visiting-wartime-israel/0000018b-3ef6-d2b8-a7db-feff186c0000</link><description>在明确谴责哈马斯恐怖活动后，美国总统拜登带着重要的政治和道德资本抵达以色列。但美以议程上仍有敏感问题</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 19:32:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-17/ty-article/.premium/why-biden-is-visiting-wartime-israel/0000018b-3ef6-d2b8-a7db-feff186c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列计划撤离黎巴嫩边境附近社区，许多人拒绝离开</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-17/ty-article/.premium/israel-plans-to-evacuate-communities-close-to-border-with-lebanon-many-refuse-to-leave/0000018b-3ef7-df22-a5eb-3fff57f10000</link><description>据《国土报》调查，居住在这些社区的 27,000 名居民中，约有 15,000 人仍留在家中。预计他们中的大多数人将很快被疏散，并被送往由以色列政府支付费用的酒店和宾馆</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 19:22:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-17/ty-article/.premium/israel-plans-to-evacuate-communities-close-to-border-with-lebanon-many-refuse-to-leave/0000018b-3ef7-df22-a5eb-3fff57f10000</guid></item><item><title>消防员从 7,500 英里外接听以色列的紧急呼叫</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-17/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-firefighters-answering-israels-emergency-call-from-7-500-miles-away/0000018b-3e66-d2b8-a7db-fe6fb67a0000</link><description>与美国志愿者一起度过一个下午，在以色列中部灭火和追赶火箭弹。目前驻扎在拉姆勒的一名加州消防员表示，“这与我在美国经历过的任何事情都不一样”</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 19:14:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-17/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-firefighters-answering-israels-emergency-call-from-7-500-miles-away/0000018b-3e66-d2b8-a7db-fe6fb67a0000</guid></item><item><title>“他写信给我：我的父母去世了，我需要帮助”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2023-10-17/ty-article-podcast/.premium/he-wrote-me-my-parents-are-dead-i-need-help/0000018b-3e82-d2b8-a7db-feef48080000</link><description></description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 19:05:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2023-10-17/ty-article-podcast/.premium/he-wrote-me-my-parents-are-dead-i-need-help/0000018b-3e82-d2b8-a7db-feef48080000</guid></item><item><title>让以色列在过度拥挤的条件下关押安全囚犯的法案获得初步批准</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-17/ty-article/.premium/bill-to-let-israel-hold-security-prisoners-in-overcrowded-conditions-gets-initial-approval/0000018b-3ed5-df22-a5eb-3ffd52930000</link><description>该法案将赋予国家安全部长 Itamar Ben-Gvir 豁免居住空间要求的权力，并让囚犯睡在地板上的床垫上</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 18:53:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-17/ty-article/.premium/bill-to-let-israel-hold-security-prisoners-in-overcrowded-conditions-gets-initial-approval/0000018b-3ed5-df22-a5eb-3ffd52930000</guid></item><item><title>以色列称伊斯兰圣战组织火箭发射失败导致加沙医院数百人死亡；哈马斯指责以色列国防军</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-17/ty-article/hundreds-killed-in-israeli-airstrike-on-gaza-city-hospital-gaza-health-ministry-says/0000018b-3ec5-dcae-afaf-7eff6ef70000</link><description>以色列国防军称录音证明伊斯兰圣战有罪；内塔尼亚胡指责“野蛮的恐怖分子”对阿赫利医院的死亡负责</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 18:22:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-17/ty-article/hundreds-killed-in-israeli-airstrike-on-gaza-city-hospital-gaza-health-ministry-says/0000018b-3ec5-dcae-afaf-7eff6ef70000</guid></item><item><title>以色列医院拒绝治疗哈马斯恐怖分子，消息人士称“民族感情”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-17/ty-article/.premium/israeli-hospital-refuses-to-treat-hamas-terrorist-sources-cite-national-feelings/0000018b-3e79-d2b8-a7db-fe7f7c320000</link><description>最近宣布的一项政策禁止公立医院治疗恐怖分子，但卫生部尚未公布明确的实施程序</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 17:33:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-17/ty-article/.premium/israeli-hospital-refuses-to-treat-hamas-terrorist-sources-cite-national-feelings/0000018b-3e79-d2b8-a7db-fe7f7c320000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡对人质的家人感到恐惧。这可能会影响他的判断</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-17/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-is-petrified-of-the-hostages-families-it-could-impact-his-judgment/0000018b-3e01-d5be-a7eb-befd1bc50000</link><description>如果战争内阁中负责的成年人不保持警惕，以色列对哈马斯的军事反应将更多地是总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡的政治算计的结果，而不是该国非常现实和紧迫的优先事项</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 15:48:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-17/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-is-petrified-of-the-hostages-families-it-could-impact-his-judgment/0000018b-3e01-d5be-a7eb-befd1bc50000</guid></item><item><title>以色列柔道运动员雅埃尔·阿拉德加入国际奥委会</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/sports/2023-10-17/ty-article/.premium/israeli-judoka-yael-arad-joins-international-olympic-committee/0000018b-3e24-d2b8-a7db-fe6f191a0000</link><description>以色列国家奥委会主席阿拉德表示，国际奥委会投票承认她在 10 月 7 日哈马斯袭击事件后具有了新的意义</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 15:31:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/sports/2023-10-17/ty-article/.premium/israeli-judoka-yael-arad-joins-international-olympic-committee/0000018b-3e24-d2b8-a7db-fe6f191a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列在吊销数百名加沙劳工的工作许可证后拘留了他们</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-17/ty-article/.premium/israel-detained-hundreds-of-gazan-laborers-after-revoking-their-work-permits/0000018b-3dbb-d582-a3cb-7dbb3dae0000</link><description>人权组织声称，政府没有拘留加沙人的法律权力，军队表示，由于战争，他们无法返回加沙，目前被拘留在约旦河西岸的一处设施中，问题仍在继续。接受检查</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 14:49:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-17/ty-article/.premium/israel-detained-hundreds-of-gazan-laborers-after-revoking-their-work-permits/0000018b-3dbb-d582-a3cb-7dbb3dae0000</guid></item><item><title>议会国家安全委员会批准新的、宽松的枪支许可证条件</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-17/ty-article/.premium/knesset-national-security-committee-approves-new-lenient-fire-arms-license-conditions/0000018b-3db7-d5be-a7eb-bfff87090000</link><description>新规定本应是临时性的，但已被定为永久性的。司法部代表：尚未审查对自杀、家庭暴力和性别相关暴力的影响</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 14:39:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-17/ty-article/.premium/knesset-national-security-committee-approves-new-lenient-fire-arms-license-conditions/0000018b-3db7-d5be-a7eb-bfff87090000</guid></item><item><title>被哈马斯扣押的法裔以色列人质的母亲：“乞求全世界带我的孩子回家”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-17/ty-article/.premium/mother-of-french-israeli-hostage-by-hamas-begging-the-world-to-bring-my-baby-home/0000018b-3d20-d101-a9ab-bf3c37aa0000</link><description>21 岁的玛雅·谢姆 (Maya Schem) 拥有法国和以色列双重国籍，在哈马斯袭击加沙边境附近的以色列社区时被哈马斯抓走。她的家人直到哈马斯在加沙发布她的视频几天后才发现她被扣为人质</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 13:48:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-17/ty-article/.premium/mother-of-french-israeli-hostage-by-hamas-begging-the-world-to-bring-my-baby-home/0000018b-3d20-d101-a9ab-bf3c37aa0000</guid></item><item><title>犹太白宫官员在访问以色列之前赞扬拜登：“这就是他”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-17/ty-article/.premium/jewish-white-house-officials-applaud-biden-ahead-of-israel-visit-this-is-who-he-is/0000018b-3d41-d450-a3af-7d5d3f590000</link><description>一名高级工作人员表示，“现在有两件事给了我力量：犹太人民的韧性以及拜登总统的领导力和道德清晰度”</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 13:43:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-17/ty-article/.premium/jewish-white-house-officials-applaud-biden-ahead-of-israel-visit-this-is-who-he-is/0000018b-3d41-d450-a3af-7d5d3f590000</guid></item><item><title>考古、圣经机构谴责哈马斯大屠杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2023-10-17/ty-article/archaeological-biblical-institutions-condemn-hamas-massacre/0000018b-3d42-d101-a9ab-bf7e03f60000</link><description>以色列考古学家抱怨一周以来他们的沉默，美国海外研究协会周一谴责哈马斯对以色列平民的“恶毒屠杀”，而圣经文学协会则对世界反犹太主义抬头表示担忧</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 13:15:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2023-10-17/ty-article/archaeological-biblical-institutions-condemn-hamas-massacre/0000018b-3d42-d101-a9ab-bf7e03f60000</guid></item></channel></rss>